# 7. この衝動に

Slade: Alright, are you ready?
Akito: Yeah, I'm ready whenever...
Slade: ♪————————!
Akito: (I felt something different while hearing him sing just now.)
Akito: (What if this is the special something that KAITO said I might come across?)
Akito: (If that's the case...)
Slade: Okay, Akito, you start us off!
Akito: Alright.
An: Phew...
An: Morning runs really are the best! They do such a great job of getting your brain going!
Kohane: Yeah, and since they get us warmed up, we can start singing as soon as we're done.
An: Yeah! We need to practice a lot more, so let's use our time wisely!
An: Because if we really are gonna set out into the world, we've gotta make use of every minute and second we have...!
An: I'm sure Akito's doing that as we speak!
Kohane: Right.
An: Huh...?
An: Do you hear that? I think it's coming from the park.
Kohane: Oh, you're right... Are people singing?
An: What if him and Toya already started practicing...? Let's go see!
Kohane: That's Shinonome... But who are those other two...?
Toya: Azusawa! Shiraishi!
An: Oh, Toya! What's going on here?
Toya: I don't know yet either. They were already singing by the time I arrived here at our normal time.
Akito: ♪————————!
Cedric & Slade: ...
Akito: (Give it your all...!)
Akito: (Sing with everything you have!)
Akito: ♪————————!
Cedric: ...
Slade: Wait.
Akito: ...!
Slade: Sorry for interrupting you. But...
Slade: What's going on? Why are you singing like that?
Akito: “What's going on”...?
Slade: Is it because it's so early in the morning? Or are you not feeling well...?
Slade: Oh, did you need a little more time to warm up? I did sorta rush you!
Cedric: Slade...
Slade: I mean...
Slade: This isn't what you really sound like, is it...?
Akito: ...
Slade: Why...?
Slade: Why aren't you saying anything?
Slade: We agreed not to hold back. Sing with everything you have. You did during that event, right...?
Akito: ...
Slade: What's going on...?
Slade: Is your resolve really that weak?
Akito: My resolve...?
Slade: You're gonna stand on top of the world, right? But you're never going to get there singing like that...
Akito: Wait, why do you know about—
Slade: Forget it.
Slade: We're gonna be the ones who stand on top of the world!
Slade: ♪————————!
Toya: (...! The way he's singing!)
Kohane: (It's so piercing and straightforward... But more importantly...)
Akito: ...
Akito: (He wasn't singing at 100% before...!)
Slade: ♪————————! ♪————————!
Akito: Whoa...
Akito: (How's he doing this...?!)
Akito: (It's like I'm being shaken from the core...!)
Slade: ♪————————!
Akito: (I'm not about to let him walk away with this.)
Akito: (I can't let things end here!!)
Akito: ♪————————————————!
Slade: ...!
Akito: (Just keep singing! Make full use of this feeling...!)
Akito: ♪————————! ♪————————!
Slade: Oh...!
Cedric: This is incredible...
Akito: Huff... Huff...
Akito: (It's been a while since I last sang like my life depended on it.)
Slade: Akito!
Akito: Whoa! Why are you—
Slade: I knew it! You can sing like a pro!!
Slade: Thank you! That was totally awesome!
Akito: Th-Thanks...
Cedric: Sorry for my brother letting his emotions get the better of him just now.
Akito: That's fine. What he said actually opened my eyes.
Cedric: Really? That's good to hear.
Akito: But more importantly... What you said about us standing on top of the world—
Cedric: I need to apologize to all of you as well. I'm sorry if we interrupted your practice.
Akito: Huh...?
Akito: Wait, you guys were already here?
Toya: Yes, but only for a little bit.
Slade: Huh? All of Vivid BAD SQUAD's here now...! I didn't notice at all...!
Slade: Whoa... There's so much I wanna ask you guys! Man, where do I even begin...?!
Cedric: We're out of time, Slade. If we don't start heading over now, we're really going to miss our flight.
Slade: Y-Yeah, I know...!
Slade: *Sigh* Then, let's go, Ceddy. Thanks for agreeing to do this with me, Akito!
Akito: Oh, you guys are leaving?
Cedric: Sorry, but we really are out of time.
Cedric: That being said, we're aiming for the same place as you, so I'm sure we'll meet again...
An: The same place...?
Slade: That's right! We need to at least tell you guys this!
Slade: You guys put on an absolutely amazing performance during RAD BLAST. But...
Slade: We're the ones who are gonna see what lies beyond Nagi's dream!
Kohane: Huh?
Slade: So, we'll be waiting for you in the states!
Slade: See you guys!
An: Was he talking about Aunt Nagi just now...?
Kohane: Yeah... We all heard the same thing just now, right?
Toya: Yes...
Akito: So many questions left unanswered...
Akito: (But...)
Akito: (I guess the world must be full of guys like them...)
Akito: (Singers who can put on unbelievable performances like it's nothing...!)
Akito: Hm...? What is it, Toya? Why are you staring at me like that?
Toya: No, it's just...
Toya: I feel like you're back to being your usual self.
Akito: Yeah, me too.
